WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.000
At this moment, in different places of the world, people are doing different things.

00:07.000 --> 00:17.000
Hey! In London, it's 5 o'clock in the afternoon, and people are leaving work and are going home.

00:17.000 --> 00:21.000
They're waiting for buses or trains.

00:21.000 --> 00:28.000
Some people are driving home. Some are getting off buses or trains.

00:28.000 --> 00:34.000
Some are having afternoon tea at home or having a drink.

00:34.000 --> 00:43.000
B. In Moscow, it's 8 o'clock in the evening, so people aren't having afternoon tea.

00:43.000 --> 00:48.000
They are having dinner at home or in restaurants.

00:48.000 --> 00:52.000
Some are going to the theatre or watching a film.

00:52.000 --> 00:59.000
Some are watching television or playing games at home.

00:59.000 --> 01:07.000
C. In Beijing, it's 1 o'clock at night, so people aren't having dinner.

01:07.000 --> 01:16.000
Most people are sleeping. Some people are still working and some are going home from work.

01:17.000 --> 01:23.000
D. In Los Angeles, it's 9 o'clock in the morning.

01:23.000 --> 01:31.000
People aren't sleeping. They're working. Children are starting their lessons.

01:31.000 --> 01:41.000
E. In New York, it's 12 o'clock. People aren't working. They're having lunch.

01:41.000 --> 01:48.000
They are eating hamburgers or hot dogs and drinking coffee or cola.

01:48.000 --> 01:53.000
Some people are seeing friends, calling home or shopping.

